headline: FIS and Oracle Enhance Utility Billing Experience
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., November 12, 2024--Global financial technology leader FIS® (NYSE: FIS) is today announcing a collaboration with Oracle to bring enhanced billing and payment capabilities to Oracle’s utility customers. The FIS BillerIQ solution running on OCI will enable the roll out of electronic bill delivery and provide a seamless, end-to-end experience from meter consumption to payment.
